{"id":"bank_source-secret-topic-spelling-niipbu","title":"SOURCE SECRET TOPIC SPELLING","category":"English Grammar & Error Spotting","group":"topic","source":"English Grammar & Error Spotting","createdAt":"2026-07-13T00:00:00.000Z","questions":[{"question":"Q101. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(c) Achivement","(a) Achievement","(b) Acheivement","(d) Achevement"],"answer":1,"explanation":"'C' ke bina wale words mein 'ie' ka use hota hai."},{"question":"Q102. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(c) Acknowlegement","(a) Aknowledgement","(b) Acknowledgement","(d) Aknowlegement"],"answer":2,"explanation":"'Knowledge' ki puri spelling ke baad 'ment' lagta hai."},{"question":"Q103. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(b) Amature","(d) Amateure","(c) Amatuer","(a) Amateur"],"answer":3,"explanation":"'Amateur' (shaukiya) mein 'eur' aata hai."},{"question":"Q104. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(d) Aniversery","(a) Anniversary","(b) Aniversary","(c) Anniversery"],"answer":1,"explanation":"'Double n' aur end mein 'ary' hota hai."},{"question":"Q105. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(b) Anonimous","(a) Anonymous","(d) Annonimous","(c) Annonymous"],"answer":1,"explanation":"'A-no-ny-mous' (Gumnaam)."},{"question":"Q106. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(b) Aperance","(d) Appearanse","(c) Apperance","(a) Appearance"],"answer":3,"explanation":"'Appear' + 'ance' (Double 'p')."},{"question":"Q107. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(c) Archialogist","(b) Archeologist","(d) Archelogist","(a) Archaeologist"],"answer":3,"explanation":"'Archae' (purana) + 'ologist'."},{"question":"Q108. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(b) Architacture","(a) Architecture","(d) Architechure","(c) Architechture"],"answer":1,"explanation":"'Ar-chi-tec-ture'."},{"question":"Q109. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(d) Arrangemant","(c) Arrangment","(a) Arrangement","(b) Arangement"],"answer":2,"explanation":"'Arrange' puri spelling + 'ment'."},{"question":"Q110. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(d) Assistense","(b) Asistance","(c) Assistanse","(a) Assistance"],"answer":3,"explanation":"'Assist' + 'ance'."},{"question":"Q111. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(a) Beginning","(d) Beginneng","(c) Begining","(b) Begining"],"answer":0,"explanation":"Stress hone par 'n' double ho jata hai."},{"question":"Q112. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(c) Benifited","(a) Benefited","(d) Benifitted","(b) Benefitted"],"answer":1,"explanation":"SSC 'Benefited' (Single 't') ko zyada sahi manta hai."},{"question":"Q113. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(d) Beveridg","(b) Beaverage","(a) Beverage","(c) Beveragee"],"answer":2,"explanation":"'Bev-er-age' (Peya padarth)."},{"question":"Q114. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(a) Boundary","(d) Boundrye","(b) Boundery","(c) Boundry"],"answer":0,"explanation":"'Bound' + 'ary'."},{"question":"Q115. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(d) Brelliant","(b) Briliant","(a) Brilliant","(c) Brillyant"],"answer":2,"explanation":"'Double l' aur 'iant' aata hai."},{"question":"Q116. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(c) Busyness","(a) Business","(b) Buisness","(d) Bussiness"],"answer":1,"explanation":"'Busy' se banta hai, isliye 'u' pehle."},{"question":"Q117. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(c) Candidat","(a) Candidate","(b) Candidate","(d) Candydate"],"answer":1,"explanation":"'Can-di-date'."},{"question":"Q118. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(d) Catagery","(c) Categary","(a) Category","(b) Catagory"],"answer":2,"explanation":"'Cat-e-go-ry'."},{"question":"Q119. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(d) Cemmetery","(b) Cemetary","(a) Cemetery","(c) Cemetry"],"answer":2,"explanation":"'Cem-e-te-ry' (Sab jagah 'e' hota hai)."},{"question":"Q120. Select the CORRECTLY spelt word.","options":["(c) Chalinge","(a) Challenge","(d) 